The '''''Journal of Epidemiology and Community Health''''' is a [[Peer review|peer-reviewed]] [[public health journal]] that covers all aspects of [[epidemiology]] and [[public health]]. It is published by the [[BMJ Group]].

== History ==
The journal was established in 1947 and has been published under various titles. Former titles are:
*1949- 1953: British Journal of Social Medicine
*1954- 1977: British Journal of Preventive and Social Medicine
*1978: Epidemiology and Community Health

